---

<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8" />
        <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
        <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
        <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
        <title>L1 — QScrape</title>
        <style>
            *,
            *::before,
            *::after {
                box-sizing: border-box;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
            }

            body {
                background: #0d0d14;
                color: #c9c9d8;
                font-family:
                    system-ui,
                    -apple-system,
                    sans-serif;
                font-size: 16px;
                line-height: 1.6;
                padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
            }

            .container {
                max-width: 720px;
                margin: 0 auto;
            }

            header {
                margin-bottom: 3rem;
                border-bottom: 1px solid #1e1e2e;
                padding-bottom: 2rem;
            }

            .breadcrumb {
                font-family: "Courier New", Courier, monospace;
                font-size: 0.85rem;
                color: #3a3a56;
                margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            }

            .breadcrumb a {
                color: #7c9fe6;
                text-decoration: none;
            }

            .breadcrumb a:hover {
                text-decoration: underline;
            }

            .logo {
                font-family: "Courier New", Courier, monospace;
                font-size: 2.5rem;
                font-weight: 700;
                color: #e2e2f0;
                letter-spacing: -0.5px;
            }

            .tagline {
                color: #6e6e8a;
                margin-top: 0.4rem;
                font-size: 0.95rem;
            }

            section {
                margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 0.75rem;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                letter-spacing: 0.12em;
                color: #5a5a78;
                margin-bottom: 1rem;
            }

            p {
                color: #a0a0b8;
                max-width: 60ch;
            }

            a {
                color: #7c9fe6;
                text-decoration: none;
            }

            a:hover {
                text-decoration: underline;
            }

            .sites {
                list-style: none;
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 0.75rem;
            }

            .site-item {
                display: block;
                padding: 0.9rem 1rem;
                color: inherit;
                border-radius: 6px;
                border: 1px solid transparent;
                transition:
                    background-color 0.2s,
                    border-color 0.2s;
            }

            .site-item:hover {
                background-color: #111120;
                border-color: #1a1a2e;
            }

            .site-header {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 0.75rem;
                margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
            }

            .site-link {
                margin-left: auto;
                color: #3a3a56;
                text-decoration: none;
                font-size: 0.85rem;
                line-height: 1;
                transition: color 0.15s;
            }

            .site-item:hover .site-link {
                color: #7c9fe6;
            }

            .site-label {
                font-family: "Courier New", Courier, monospace;
                font-size: 0.8rem;
                font-weight: 600;
                color: #e2e2f0;
                white-space: nowrap;
            }

            .site-name {
                color: #b0b0cc;
                font-size: 0.9rem;
                font-weight: 500;
            }

            .site-desc {
                color: #7a7a96;
                font-size: 0.9rem;
            }

            .badge-live {
                font-size: 0.65rem;
                font-weight: 700;
                text-transform: uppercase;
                letter-spacing: 0.08em;
                background: #1a3a1a;
                color: #4caf76;
                border: 1px solid #2a5a2a;
                padding: 0.15em 0.5em;
                border-radius: 3px;
                white-space: nowrap;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="container">
            <header>
                <div class="breadcrumb">
                    <a href="/">QScrape</a> / L1
                </div>
                <div class="logo">Level 1</div>
                <div class="tagline">Standard HTML/CSS/JS — no dynamic data, no web frameworks</div>
            </header>

            <section>
                <h2>About</h2>
                <p>
                    L1 sites are static pages built with <a href="https://astro.build/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Astro</a>.
                    All content is rendered at build time into plain HTML. There are no client-side
                    frameworks, no API calls, and no anti-scraping measures. These sites serve as
                    a baseline to verify that a scraper can correctly parse real-world HTML structure,
                    navigate multi-page sites, and extract structured data.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>Sites</h2>
                <ul class="sites">
                    <li>
                        <a class="site-item" href="/l1/news/">
                            <div class="site-header">
                                <span class="site-label">/l1/news</span>
                                <span class="badge-live">LIVE</span>
                                <span class="site-link">↗</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="site-name">Mountainhome Herald</div>
                            <div class="site-desc">News portal with article listings, individual articles, and an about page. Tests pagination and article extraction.</div>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a class="site-item" href="/l1/scoretap/">
                            <div class="site-header">
                                <span class="site-label">/l1/scoretap</span>
                                <span class="badge-live">LIVE</span>
                                <span class="site-link">↗</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="site-name">ScoreTap</div>
                            <div class="site-desc">Esports scores and match results. Tests structured tabular data, team/event relationships, and linked detail pages.</div>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <a class="site-item" href="/l1/taxes/">
                            <div class="site-header">
                                <span class="site-label">/l1/taxes</span>
                                <span class="badge-live">LIVE</span>
                                <span class="site-link">↗</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="site-name">Eldoria Registry of Deeds</div>
                            <div class="site-desc">Property tax records and deed search. Tests form-like search interfaces, record listings, and document viewer pages.</div>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </section>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
